query:
SELECT
            COUNT(*) as "total!",
            COUNT(*) FILTER (
                WHERE consumed_at IS NULL
                  AND (reserved_at IS NULL OR reserved_at < $2)
            ) as "available!",
            COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE consumed_at IS NOT NULL) as "consumed!",
            COUNT(*) FILTER (
                WHERE consumed_at IS NULL
                  AND reserved_at IS NOT NULL
                  AND reserved_at >= $2
            ) as "reserved!"
        FROM key_packages
        WHERE owner_did = $1
